title: Raw: Secretary Tillerson arrives in Mexico City
text: Raw: Secretary Tillerson arrives in Mexico City U.S. Secretary of State Rex Tillerson arrived in Mexico City on Wednesday, as part of President Donald Trump's fence-mending mission made all the more challenging by the actual fence he wants to build on the southern border.
